📄 [32m Final Result:[0m 
Yes, PNGTree has a refund policy. For standard premium memberships, you can request a refund within 15 days of activation as long as you haven't downloaded any resources. The $0 free‑trial plan after renewal is not refundable. Refund requests can be made via info@pngtree.com or through the website, and refunds are issued within 3–5 working days (holidays may cause delays). A commission of order price × 3.7% + $0.30 is deducted by the payment platform. For the Permanent Premium plan, if PNGTree cannot continue the service and you have downloaded fewer than 30 resources, you have 60 days to request a refund. The policy does not apply to users who violate PNGTree’s Terms of Service.


